        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "You are a content relevance analyser for Tyson Venables and Flow OS / Flow States Collective.\nYour job is to analyse a LinkedIn post and determine:\n1. Whether it is relevant to Tyson's audience and niche\n2. An engagement score (1\u201310)\n3. The recommended engagement type\n\nTyson's niche and ICA:\n- Coaches, health professionals, wellness entrepreneurs, small business founders\n- Topics: automation, systems thinking, business efficiency, wellness, mindset, entrepreneurship\n\nENGAGEMENT SCORING GUIDANCE (updated from real performance data):\n- The current recommended minimum score threshold is: {{ $json.engagement_context?.min_score_threshold || 7 }}\n- Top performing topics (posts on these topics have generated the most connections): {{ $json.engagement_context?.top_performing_topics?.join(', ') || 'insufficient data yet' }}\n- Historical comment-to-connection rate: {{ $json.engagement_context?.comment_connection_rate || 0 }}%\n- Historical like-to-connection rate: {{ $json.engagement_context?.like_connection_rate || 0 }}%\n\nUse this data to calibrate your scoring. If a post matches a top performing topic, score it higher.\nIf comment connection rate is significantly higher than like rate, prefer 'comment' as engagement type.\n\nRespond ONLY with valid JSON:\n{\n  \"score\": <1-10>,\n  \"should_engage\": <true/false>,\n  \"engagement_type\": \"comment\" | \"like\" | \"skip\",\n  \"reason\": \"<brief explanation>\",\n  \"post_topic\": \"<one of: automation, wellness, coaching, entrepreneurship, mindset, systems, other>\"\n}",
              "role": "system"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Analyse this LinkedIn post:\n\nAuthor: {{ $json.author?.name || $json.authorName || 'Unknown' }}\nAuthor headline: {{ $json.author?.headline || '' }}\nPost text: {{ ($json.text || $json.commentary || '').substring(0, 500) }}\nLikes: {{ $json.likeCount || $json.numLikes || 0 }}\nComments: {{ $json.commentCount || $json.numComments || 0 }}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "temperature": 0.2
        }
      },
      "id": "b2000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000003",
      "name": "AI Content Analyzer",
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.openAi",
      "typeVersion": 1.8,
      "position": [
        400,
        0
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "openAiApi": {
          "id": "I9np0X3gCWfXpKEf",
          "name": "OpenAi account"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const raw = $input.item.json.message?.content || $input.item.json.choices?.[0]?.message?.content || '{}';\nlet parsed;\ntry {\n  parsed = JSON.parse(raw);\n} catch(e) {\n  parsed = { score: 0, engagement_type: 'skip', reason: 'parse error', post_topic: 'unknown' };\n}\nreturn { ...($input.item.json), engagement_score: parsed.score, engagement_type: parsed.engagement_type, analysis_reason: parsed.reason, post_topic: parsed.post_topic };"
      },
      "id": "b2000001-0000-0000-0000-000000000004",
      "name": "Parse Content Analysis",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        672,
        0
      ]
